      • getQubeID

        public java.lang.String getQubeID(java.lang.String net,
                                  java.util.GregorianCalendar originTime,
                                  double lat,
                                  double lon)
        Get a EventID from a Qube message stored in the qml.qube table which matches the given network, origintime and location.
        Parameters:
        net - Two character network code per qube (lower case fdsn code)
        originTime - The origin time of this quake
        lat - Latitude
        lon - Longitude
        Returns:
        Null if no matching quake is found, else the local event id
